title: Home Depot: Kids’ Table and Chair Set Only $34.99 Shipped (Regularly $69.98)
text:
Need a table for the kiddos? Head on over to The Home Depot where you can get one of these cute Teamson 24.25″ Table and Chair Sets in White or Pink for only $34.99 shipped (regularly $69.98).

This wooden table is hand painted with non-toxic paint and hand carved. This would make the perfect spot for drawing, snacking and more!
(Thanks, Brenna!)
